GrowRig Hardware — Licensing intent
====================================

This repository currently holds early-stage concepts and design notes. The
intended licensing, to be finalized as projects mature, is:

  - Hardware designs (schematics, PCB, mechanical): CERN-OHL-S v2 (or similar
    open-hardware license). See https://ohwr.org/project/cernohl
  - Firmware and software: a permissive OSS license (MIT or Apache-2.0).
  - Documentation and design notes: CC BY-SA 4.0.

Until per-project LICENSE files are added, treat everything here as
"all rights reserved, open-source intended" — reach out before redistributing.